#, no-wrap
msgid "    $paymentMethod = $user->defaultPaymentMethod();\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/8.x/billing.md:388
msgid ""
"You can retrieve a specific payment method that is attached to the billable "
"model using the `findPaymentMethod` method:"
